ry type with `PathInits` constructor (`BeanPath`)\n    - typed query type without `PathInits` constructor (`SimplePath`)\n    - non-typed query type with `PathInits` constructor (`NonTypedPathWithInits`)\n    - non-typed query type without `PathInits` constructor (`StringPath`)\n  - Uses public Querydsl APIs (`Expressions.listPath(...).any()`) rather than direct reflection.\n  - Verifies `COLLECTION_ANY` metadata and constructor path behavior.\n\n- Updated `Querydsl_coreTest` to be a public top-level test class.\n\nTests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a75812b0c7affc00169f9298d76a8819485de51456850e819\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 453, "output": 1037, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 34258, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777936767346, "responseId": "resp_0a75812b0c7affc00169f9297fd1a481948368e2d716bdb615"}, "toolResults": []}
